  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dot Hop is a grid-based puzzle game. Find a path from start to end without leaving any dots behind. You can't move backwards, but you can hop over dots you've already dotted. Some of these can get pretty hard, but the knots are  satisfying to unravel. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dot Hop has 72 puzzles and over 1000 dots to be hopped.  The puzzles have been created by hand, but a generator is in the works, along with more mechanics and game modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras/d6854cc9aefbe23b5781cba25e9827a5.avif?t=1759440344\" alt=\"Dot Hop's main menu. Buttons read: Start, Options, Puzzles, Gym, Credits, Quit.\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras_big/d6854cc9aefbe23b5781cba25e9827a5.webp?t=1759440344 width=1600 height=979 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras/a41cf0e9d084c8647e3343470ea27dc3.avif?t=1759440344\" alt=\"Dot Hop's tutorial theme: hop between blue donuts to reach the goal.\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras_big/a41cf0e9d084c8647e3343470ea27dc3.webp?t=1759440344 width=1600 height=979 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras/0da69b7b434d41f2d610b1ab9cc3eedc.avif?t=1759440344\" alt=\"Dot Hop's spring theme: Bushes with small flowers on them.\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras_big/0da69b7b434d41f2d610b1ab9cc3eedc.webp?t=1759440344 width=1600 height=979 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras/352e780b3a8e7d03f776b1d010800ae7.avif?t=1759440344\" alt=\"Dot Hop's snow theme - hop across snowmen to reach the goal.\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras_big/352e780b3a8e7d03f776b1d010800ae7.webp?t=1759440344 width=1600 height=979 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras/84be29f0dda609006543784759bd782b.avif?t=1759440344\" alt=\"Dot Hop's Space theme: Play as a spaceship, hop across asteroids, try to reach the star.\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras_big/84be29f0dda609006543784759bd782b.webp?t=1759440344 width=1600 height=979 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras/14aa9293cefeb231356f6f60d08b9e05.avif?t=1759440344\" alt=\"Dot Hop's hardest puzzle with the \"All The Dots\" theme. Pumpkins, Snowmen, Sandcastles, space rocks, and blue circles fill a grid.\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras_big/14aa9293cefeb231356f6f60d08b9e05.webp?t=1759440344 width=1600 height=1008 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras/5b9efa1b08a9bd09982f361bc64d36a1.avif?t=1759440344\" alt=\"Dot Hop's Puzzle Gym showing an All The Dots themed puzzle.\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras_big/5b9efa1b08a9bd09982f361bc64d36a1.webp?t=1759440344 width=1600 height=979 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dot Hop is a grid-based puzzle game. Find a path from start to end without leaving any dots behind. You can't move backwards, but you can hop over dots you've already dotted. Some of these can get pretty hard, but the knots are  satisfying to unravel. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dot Hop has 72 puzzles and over 1000 dots to be hopped.  The puzzles have been created by hand, but a generator is in the works, along with more mechanics and game modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras/d6854cc9aefbe23b5781cba25e9827a5.avif?t=1759440344\" alt=\"Dot Hop's main menu. Buttons read: Start, Options, Puzzles, Gym, Credits, Quit.\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras_big/d6854cc9aefbe23b5781cba25e9827a5.webp?t=1759440344 width=1600 height=979 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras/a41cf0e9d084c8647e3343470ea27dc3.avif?t=1759440344\" alt=\"Dot Hop's tutorial theme: hop between blue donuts to reach the goal.\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras_big/a41cf0e9d084c8647e3343470ea27dc3.webp?t=1759440344 width=1600 height=979 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras/0da69b7b434d41f2d610b1ab9cc3eedc.avif?t=1759440344\" alt=\"Dot Hop's spring theme: Bushes with small flowers on them.\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2779710/extras_big/0da69b7b434d41f2d610b1ab9cc3eedc.webp?t=1759440344 width=1600 height=979 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"ht